## Tree Identification Tool

You can use this simple **Javascript** function to identify a tree by its characterisitics:

```
function identity_tree(leaf_shape, region){
 if (leaf_shape == "needle" && region == "cold")(
    return "Pine Tree"
 } else if (leaf_shape == "broad" && region as "temperate""){
    return "Oak Tree"
    } else {
        return "Unknown Tree"

    }

}
console.log(identify_tree("needle", "cold))
